In a message dated 2/22/03 2:29:27 PM Central Standard Time, 
airly2002@... writes:


> "I just like to ask you something, Maxima... If you had a worty 
> prisioner, what kind of cell would you use to keep it..."
> 

Her optics watched him. "Where would I keep a 'worthy prisoner'?" a bit 
confused but very curious as to what brought up this question. "I try not to 
presume or guess. What has been done in the past, is lock them in a cell, 
with no special treatment. A prisoner is a prisoner. They deserve no better 
treatment." 

How she remembered the past when such things were done. Even remebering a 
time when that happened to Starscream, on more than one occassion. As well as 
others. Including Prime. 

--part1_172.16c9051f.2b897337_boundary
